MANNING et al., Respondents, v. BECK et al., Appellants. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. March 27, 1894.) Action by George G. Manning and others against Lewis P. Beck and others.

Argued before DWIGHT, P. J., and LEWIS, HAIGHT, and BRADLEY, JJ.

No opinion. Judgment appealed from affirmed, with costs.
